{As Ted mentioned, our cash burn in June included a one-time principal payment of nearly $50 million related to an amendment of our PDP financing facility in conjunction with our Airbus aircraft deferral agreement.} 

翻译为：
{正如Ted所提，我们六月的现金流支出包括一笔近5000万美元的一次性本金支付，与我们与空客的飞机推迟协议相关的PDP融资设施的修改有关。}

{As Ted mentioned, our cash burn in June included a one-time principal payment of nearly $50 million related to an amendment of our PDP financing facility in conjunction with our Airbus aircraft deferral agreement.}

翻译为中文：

{如Ted所提，我们在六月的现金流出中包括了一次近5000万美元的一次性本金支付，这与我们对空客飞机延期协议的PDP融资设施修订有关。}
